article_title: Totino-Grace's Flomo ready for big battle
article_text:
Local

The Archdiocese of St. Paul and Minneapolis filed its financial reorganization plan in bankruptcy court, offering a strategy for regaining financial stability while compensating an expected 400 clergy abuse claims.
